Spring Profile (Environment Specific Files)


application-local.properties
application-dev.properties
application-staging.properties
application-prod.properties

spring.profiles.active=staging

(1) Using Command Line
We can pass profile information to Spring Boot using the switch through command prompt —spring.profiles.active=development,staging

java -jar javadevjournal.jar -Dspring.config.additional-location="external_file_location"

java -jar javadevjournal.jar -—spring.profiles.active=development,staging

java -jar ./target/employee-service.jar  --spring.profiles.active=local

